				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Thanh-T%C3%A2m-t%C3%A0i-nh%C3%A2n/B%E1%BA%A1c-m%E1%BB%87nh-o%C3%A1n/poem-8GS_o143UmqNkzGwSkKurQ">Bạc mệnh oán - 薄命怨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Thanh-T%C3%A2m-t%C3%A0i-nh%C3%A2n/author-Ry0GXj_uifS6AejvZUIukQ">Thanh Tâm tài nhân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Qu%C3%A1ch-Ch%E1%BA%A5n/C%E1%BB%95-ki%E1%BA%BFm-thi%C3%AAn/poem-QI3G67TAzoF9vJ5tN0OoUw">Cổ kiếm thiên - 古劍篇</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Qu%C3%A1ch-Ch%E1%BA%A5n/author-zaHRNLeei7-aJDxMuEaPqQ">Quách Chấn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Cu%E1%BB%93ng-phu/poem-Kf3HDgrFrYAhvjU_0G8SQQ">Cuồng phu - 狂夫</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/%C4%90%C3%B4ng-nguy%E1%BB%87t-do-Qu%E1%BA%A3ng-%C4%90%C3%B4ng-thu%E1%BB%B7-tr%C3%ACnh-v%C3%A3ng-Qu%E1%BA%A3ng-T%C3%A2y-t%E1%BB%89nh-h%E1%BB%99i-th%E1%BB%89nh-phong-s%E1%BB%A9-th%E1%BB%A7-l%E1%BB%99-ti%E1%BA%BFn-kinh-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o/poem-U6vJaArOxUZuhzMZnVEYTg">Đông nguyệt do Quảng Đông thuỷ trình vãng Quảng Tây tỉnh, hội thỉnh phong sứ thủ lộ tiến kinh đạo trung ngâm đồng Ngô Hoàng lưỡng phó sứ, thứ lạp ông tam thập vận kỳ 11 - 冬月由廣東水程往廣西省會請封使取路進京道中吟同吳黃兩副使次笠翁三十韻其十一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/author-il2-xU_Q-nIFla-ypApHCA">Trịnh Hoài Đức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Thu-C%E1%BA%A9n/Gi%C3%A1-c%C3%B4-thi%C3%AAn/poem-G0sNmDdyQqTKq53DrGzZWg">Giá cô thiên - 鷓鴣天</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Thu-C%E1%BA%A9n/author-X-40K1XlrcoKqxDGwb5eHg">Thu Cẩn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-T%C3%B4ng-Nguy%C3%AAn/Nam-gi%E1%BA%A3n-trung-%C4%91%E1%BB%81/poem-GPPhFlDbIe5Qbvv-eeKJog">Nam giản trung đề - 南澗中題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-T%C3%B4ng-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-cFCa0wn9ZwJZJ5nwtlsQmQ">Liễu Tông Nguyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/Thanh-minh/poem-3YDWV6YBQVyQBygAwpaO-g">Thanh minh - 清明</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-Vi-t%E1%BA%A3-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-zYImYpb82xchstT0tz3scQ">Thướng Vi tả tướng nhị thập vận - 上韋左相二十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Cao/T%E1%BB%B1-ph%E1%BA%ADn-ca/poem-5pG21Opvfb66SZjM6ZPeLQ">Tự phận ca - 自分歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Cao/author-C1VQ72lNTKL4OeInJcXgDw">Nguyễn Cao</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Chu-Trinh/Xu%E1%BA%A5t-%C4%91%C3%B4-m%C3%B4n/poem-cVkNAak-v8HIDIc9nZn87A">Xuất đô môn - 出都門</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Chu-Trinh/author-WLQpVVlxI3bhRBsoRr4SCw">Phan Chu Trinh</a>)<br></div>	</div>
